column5: Any good crappie lakes around Sioux Lookout? So I know its walleye country, but this year I want to try something different maybe. Going out and targeting some crappie for a few hours might be fun. Don't care about spots, just some good lakes. I wish I could find a survey site like MNDNR has.
Closest would be wabigoon/dinorwic.cedar lake north of vermilion bay also has crappies.
